de.targodan.usb.data

Class Report

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.targodan.usb.data.Report

  • public class Report
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents reports by rats like "fr+" and so on. Note: This class has some unexpected behaviour when it comes to the equal method.
    See Also:
    equals(java.lang.Object)
